{"tid":798996,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【HOSTVIEW】不要再說「富不過三代」了！現實是「捱窮捱七代」！","createTime":"2018-08-29T16:54:03.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-04T02:49:43.000Z","uid":86509,"like":22,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"8b06504901841706bb82beaaa8668d5f993edb0d","tid":798996,"uid":86509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-29T16:54:03.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=333316260740891&amp;id=575108459181042\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Fstory.php%3Fstory_fbid%3D333316260740891%26id%3D575108459181042&d=DrR9uo9Dyncmg9gRK597jQtTNu1qqkxUxYmVHECffP4%3D&h=79a01ba2\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=333316260740891&amp;id=575108459181042</a><br />\n<br />\n【HOSTVIEW】不要再說「富不過三代」了！現實是「捱窮捱七代」！<br />\n<br />\n中國民間雖然有「富不過三代」之說，但事實其實正好相反，窮人要捱窮，豈止捱足三代？經合組織最新報告指出，原來低收入家庭平均需要4.5代才能脫貧。在中國，窮人更加要捱足七代，而且與父母的教育程度有很大關連。不過，Candy就以「粘天花」及「粘地板」的理論反駁，認為富或貧，其實最大程度最決於個人，若果生性敗家，即使父母輩留下金山銀山，都只會坐食山崩。<br />\n<br />\n＃富不過三代 #現實是 #捱窮捱七代 #會過去的 #stickyceiling #stickyfloor #環球金融快線"},{"pid":"898e4c67a40357cdedb6426236b15fb0648e017e","tid":798996,"uid":177089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-29T16:55:17.000Z","msg":"點計出嚟"},{"pid":"c9469675def9c0a8c27b2eb485ea04d16cc33059","tid":798996,"uid":15815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-29T17:04:25.000Z","msg":"三十年一代<br />\n冇咩有錢佬係中國玩到過百年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f8aaed5cd1f0127b74ab909b62bb5875ae7649c7","tid":798996,"uid":19262,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-29T17:16:37.000Z","msg":"窮不過三代個解釋好似係因為三代之後已經冇後人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> （唔記得邊度睇翻黎）"},{"pid":"f576e344d505eb0a1958acd0132e75b1c44da11d","tid":798996,"uid":60049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-29T17:23:39.000Z","msg":"窮同低收入嘅分別係咩"},{"pid":"82514d8fa3042c5c47a09f